  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/588730/extras/eb6045b0773ba2e3f525a502cae00213.avif?t=1726860776\" width=600 height=250 /></span><br><br>Lariat the witch will make your wish will come true if you win a game of trivia, but if you lose, something dark will happen instead. How many lives will your ignorance ruin?<br><br>Majotori is a narratrivia, an original little game that combines an interactive narrative with a quiz game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 25+ characters<br></li><li> 50+ branching storylines<br></li><li> 1000+ engaging questions for the modern geek<br></li><li> 4 question categories (video games, cinema, animation, miscellaneous) with customizable frequency of appearance<br></li><li> A character dying a horrible death because you don't watch enough anime</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/588730/extras/eb6045b0773ba2e3f525a502cae00213.avif?t=1726860776\" width=600 height=250 /></span><br><br>Lariat the witch will make your wish will come true if you win a game of trivia, but if you lose, something dark will happen instead. How many lives will your ignorance ruin?<br><br>Majotori is a narratrivia, an original little game that combines an interactive narrative with a quiz game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 25+ characters<br></li><li> 50+ branching storylines<br></li><li> 1000+ engaging questions for the modern geek<br></li><li> 4 question categories (video games, cinema, animation, miscellaneous) with customizable frequency of appearance<br></li><li> A character dying a horrible death because you don't watch enough anime</li></ul>",
